The '''Chilean Cycling Federation''' (in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]: ''Federación Ciclista de Chile'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Chile]].

It is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and [[Confederacion Panamericana de Ciclismo|COPACI]].

