'''Club Social y Deportivo Lautaro de Buin''' is a Chilean [[Football club]], their home town is [[Buin, Chile|Buin]], [[Chile]]. They currently play in the fourth level of Chilean football, the [[Chilean Tercera División|Tercera División]].

The club were founded on ''January 23, 1923'' and participated for 10 years in [[Tercera División A de Chile|Tercera División A]] and 17 years in [[Tercera División B de Chile|Tercera División B]].

==Seasons played==
*'''12''' ''seasons'' in ''[[Tercera División A de Chile|Tercera División A]]''
*'''17''' ''seasons'' in ''[[Tercera División B de Chile|Tercera División B]]''

