{{multiple image | width = 180 | footer = [[Sport shooting]] as a whole is one of the largest and most popular sports in the world. | image1 = Vincent Hancock at 2008 Summer Olympics men's skeet finals 2008-08-16.JPG | image2 = UN Members Flags.JPG }}
This is a '''list of national and international shooting sports organizations''' who promote [[Shooting sport|sport shooting]] to civilian sport shooters, hunters, police, military and/or military reservists.
== International governing bodies == [[File:Continents.svg|thumb|right|Map of the world.]]
* [[Amateur Trapshooting Association]] (ATA)<ref>[http://www.shootata.com/ Amateur Trapshooting Association]</ref> * [[Cowboy Mounted Shooting Association]] (CMSA)<ref>[https://www.cmsaevents.com/ CMSA - Cowboy Mounted Shooting Association]</ref> * [[Fédération Internationale de Tir aux Armes Sportives de Chasse]] (FITASC)<ref>[https://www.fitasc.com/ Fédération Internationale de Tir aux Armes Sportives de Chasse]</ref> English: ''International Shooting Federation for Hunting Sports'' * [[Federation of Associations for Hunting and Conservation of the EU]] (FACE)<ref>[http://www.face.eu/ FACE: The European Federation of Associations for Hunting & Conservation]</ref> * [[Interallied Confederation of Reserve Officers]] (CIOR)<ref>[http://www.cior.net/Projects-and-activities/Military-Competition.aspx CIOR | Interallied Confederation of Reserve Officers]</ref> * [[International Benchrest Shooters]] (IBS)<ref>[http://internationalbenchrest.com/ International Benchrest Shooters]</ref> * [[International Biathlon Union]] (IBU)<ref>[http://www.biathlonworld.com/ International Biathlon Union]</ref> * [[International Confederation of Fullbore Rifle Associations]] (ICFRA)<ref>[http://www.icfra.com/ International Confederation of Fullbore Rifle Associations]</ref> * [[International Confederation of Revolver Enthusiasts]] (ICORE)<ref>[http://www.icore.org International Confederation of Revolver Enthusiasts]</ref> * [[International Crossbow Shooting Union]] (ICU),<ref>[http://www.iau-crossbow.org/ International Crossbow Shooting Union]</ref> German: ''International Armbrustschützen Union'' (IAU) * [[International Defensive Pistol Association]] (IDPA) <ref>[http://www.idpa.com/ International Defensive Pistol Association]</ref> * [[International Gallery Rifle Federation]] (IGRF) * [[International Hunting Rifle Shooting Association]] (IHRSA)<ref>[http://internationalhuntingrifleshootingassociation.com/ International Hunting Rifle Shooting Association]</ref> * [[International Metallic Silhouette Shooting Union]] (IMSSU)<ref>[http://www.imssu.org/ International Metallic Silhouette Shooting Union]</ref> * [[International Military Sports Council]] (IMSC)<ref>[http://www.cismmilsport.org/ International Military Sports Council]</ref> French: ''Conseil International du Sport Militaire'' (CISM) * [[International Police Sports Union]] (USIP),<ref>[http://internationalpolicesports.com/ International Police Sports Union (USIP)]</ref> French: ''Union Sportive Internationale des Polices'', Spanish: ''Unión Deportiva Policial Internacional'' * [[International Practical Shooting Confederation]] (IPSC)<ref>[http://www.ipsc.org/ International Practical Shooting Confederation]</ref> * [[International Shooting Sport Federation]] (ISSF),<ref>[http://www.issf-sports.org/ International Shooting Sport Federation]</ref> formerly known as UTI from French: ''L’Union Internationale des Fédérations et Associations nationals de Tir'' (UTI), or in English: ''International Union of National Shooting Federations and Associations''. * [[International T-Class Confederation]] (ITCC)<ref>[http://t-class.org International T-Class Confederation]</ref> * [[Muzzle Loaders Associations International Committee]] (MLAIC)<ref>[http://mlaic.org/ Muzzle Loaders Associations International Committee]</ref> * [[Single Action Shooting Society]] (SASS)<ref>[http://sassnet.com/ Single Action Shooting Society]</ref> * [[Steel Challenge|Steel Challenge Shooting Association]] (SCSA)<ref>[http://steelchallenge.com/ Steel Challenge Shooting Association]</ref> * [[Union Internationale de Pentathlon Moderne]] (UIPM), (English: ''International Modern Pentathlon Union'') * [[World Archery Federation]] (WA),<ref>[http://www.worldarchery.org/ World Archery Federation]</ref> formerly known as FITA from French: ''Fédération Internationale de Tir à l'Arc'' * [[World Association PPC 1500]] (WA1500) * [[World Benchrest Shooting Federation]] (WBSF)<ref>[http://www.world-benchrest.com/ World Benchrest Shooting Federation]</ref> * [[World Crossbow Shooting Association]] (WCSA)<ref>[http://www.worldcrossbow.com/ World Crossbow Shooting Association]</ref> * [[World Fast Draw Association]] (WFDA)<ref>[http://www.fastdraw.org/ World Fast Draw Association]</ref> * [[World Field Target Federation]] (WFTF)<ref>[http://www.world-field-target-federation.com/ World Field Target Federation]</ref> * [[World Forum on the Future of Sport Shooting Activities]] (WFSA)<ref>[http://wfsa.net/about-wfsa/ About WFSA : WFSA]</ref> * [[International Paralympic Committee|World Shooting Para Sport]],<ref>[https://www.paralympic.org/shooting World Shooting Para Sport]</ref> part of the [[International Paralympic Committee]] * [[World Rimfire and Air Rifle Benchrest Federation]] (WRABF)<ref>[http://www.wrabf.com/ World Rimfire and Air Rifle Benchrest Federation]</ref>
